1
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:01,000
I'm sorry, Master.

2
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:02,039
Useless.

3
00:01:03,439 --> 00:01:04,680
I, your Master, will handle this myself.

4
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:16,120
A worthy opponent at last!

5
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:10,800
Sigh.

6
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,120
I concede defeat.

7
00:02:26,199 --> 00:02:27,680
Next!

8
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,400
Next!

9
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,479
Next!

10
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:11,800
Next!

11
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:15,120
Next!

12
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:17,840
Next!

13
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,199
Next!

14
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:35,719
The legendary AlphaGo.

15
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:41,400
Prince!

16
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,120
Prince!

17
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:42,520
This is bad!

18
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:44,400
Stop bothering me.

19
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:44,960
But, Prince...

20
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:48,199
This is...

21
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,199
from every Go player in the city,

22
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:49,759
a joint

23
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:50,800
petition.

24
00:03:59,599 --> 00:04:00,400
What do you mean?

25
00:04:00,639 --> 00:04:02,319
The players want you to challenge him,

26
00:04:02,479 --> 00:04:03,479
and win back the Rank Plaque.

27
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,840
We're finally going to meet.

28
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,479
But...

29
00:04:07,479 --> 00:04:09,319
what if he doesn't show up tomorrow?

30
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,840
He'll definitely come.

31
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,520
You're that certain?

32
00:04:17,439 --> 00:04:17,879
Because

33
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,199
he would never tolerate

34
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:21,279
anyone being stronger than him.

35
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,360
So it's you.

36
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:35,240
I'm here to take back what's mine.

37
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,680
You think you can beat me?

38
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,360
Light the incense.

39
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,040
To deal with you,

40
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:42,879
that won't be necessary.

41
00:05:06,879 --> 00:05:07,680
Kosumi.

42
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,600
Ikken Tobi.

43
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,839
You lost.

44
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,600
Oh.

45
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:27,920
Is that so?

46
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:35,639
Impossible.

47
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,720
Wasting my time.

48
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:39,879
Guards!

49
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:40,680
Arrest him!

50
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,560
Hold on.

51
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,000
What's going on?

52
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,439
Which one is the real one?

53
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:52,160
After all these years,

54
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,759
instead of studying Go diligently,

55
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:57,439
you're still using this foul Trickery.

56
00:05:57,879 --> 00:05:58,680
Absurd.

57
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,720
A bet's a bet, fair and square.

58
00:06:01,959 --> 00:06:02,639
You lost,

59
00:06:02,639 --> 00:06:04,360
and that's that.

60
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:05,879
Everyone, look here.

61
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,600
Ah!

62
00:06:08,759 --> 00:06:10,319
Someone's cheating!

63
00:06:10,319 --> 00:06:11,040
Why did it change color?

64
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:11,639
How amazing!

65
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,000
Hey!

66
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:13,800
This is Trickery.

67
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:14,639
It's all fake.

68
00:06:14,639 --> 00:06:15,519
Fake!

69
00:06:15,519 --> 00:06:16,000
How could this be?

70
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,319
How could he cheat?

71
00:06:17,319 --> 00:06:18,720
How can anyone cheat at Go?

72
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,040
Everyone, look closely.

73
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:21,399
Your Prince of Chen

74
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:22,879
mixed into the game's stones

75
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:25,639
these pieces containing magnetic poles.

76
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:28,279
Sprinkle black powder, and they change color.

77
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:31,879
It really changed!

78
00:06:31,879 --> 00:06:33,079
It changed colors!

79
00:06:33,879 --> 00:06:34,720
How could this be?

80
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,319
Now look, who is that?

81
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,360
Hey!

82
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,160
Look, everyone!

83
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:45,560
Isn't that Go Master Zhang who challenged the Prince of Chen last year?

84
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:47,600
I've seen this man at the Go parlor in west town.

85
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:48,920
I've seen him play Go with others.

86
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,600
He's the genius Zhang Shaoqian!

87
00:06:50,959 --> 00:06:51,519
Hey, hey, hey!

88
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:52,560
I recognize him.

89
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:55,680
Isn't he that prodigy who was famous a few years back?

90
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,759
Exactly.

91
00:06:57,680 --> 00:07:00,399
All of them once challenged your Prince of Chen,

92
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,000
and they all won.

93
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:05,040
But sadly, your Prince of Chen refused to admit it,

94
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:07,319
and threw them all into prison instead.

95
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,279
That's impossible.

96
00:07:08,519 --> 00:07:10,279
Our Prince of Chen is the God of Go.

97
00:07:10,279 --> 00:07:11,279
How could that be?

98
00:07:11,759 --> 00:07:15,759
Because the Prince of Chen before you is a fake.

99
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:16,839
Huh?

100
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:17,639
Fake?

101
00:07:17,879 --> 00:07:19,480
And the real Prince of Chen

102
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,920
is actually this man right beside me.

103
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:25,720
Three years ago, your fake Prince used this same deceitful trick

104
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,560
to defeat the real Prince of Chen,

105
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:28,160
and then locked him away in prison.

106
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,399
All these years,

107
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:31,160
he's been impersonating the Prince of Chen.

108
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:31,879
You're lying!

109
00:07:31,879 --> 00:07:33,079
Citizens, take a good look.

110
00:07:33,079 --> 00:07:34,920
Who is truly your real Prince?

111
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,560
A fake!

112
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,600
He's a fake!

113
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:50,600
Phew.

114
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,399
The mission's finally done.

115
00:07:57,879 --> 00:07:58,160
Prince of Chen,

116
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:01,000
are you really going

117
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,759
to return to the palace with us as Emperor?

118
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,000
You think I was lying to you?

119
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,040
Don't you want to change your mind?

120
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:10,480
Don't you want to stay and protect your people,

121
00:08:10,519 --> 00:08:12,759
and stay here studying your Go manuals?

122
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,399
Hmm?

123
00:08:14,399 --> 00:08:15,399
What are you...

124
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:18,319
I...

125
00:08:18,519 --> 00:08:19,319
Ah.

126
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,600
It's just that

127
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,839
no Prince has ever truly kept his word.

128
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:25,720
Sigh.

129
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,959
Now that my own affairs are settled,

130
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,319
naturally, the next step

131
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,879
is to fulfill my own promise.

132
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,159
Let's go.

133
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:51,960
Oh dear.

134
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:54,080
How did it come to this?

135
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:54,480
Hmph.

136
00:08:56,679 --> 00:08:58,519
You came to laugh at me, didn't you?

137
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,080
Not at all.

138
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:04,799
I've been waiting here for the Prince for a long time.

139
00:09:20,759 --> 00:09:21,559
Oh my

140
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:22,919
Hey

141
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:23,879
Hey, driver

142
00:09:24,279 --> 00:09:25,320
Let me ask you something

143
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,360
How far is Kangcheng?

144
00:09:26,759 --> 00:09:28,759
About sixty more li, I'd say

145
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:29,960
Sixty li, huh

146
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:30,600
Then how about this

147
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:32,360
Tomorrow, take a detour around Kangcheng

148
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,879
Why are you making the driver detour?

149
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,399
Don't tell me

150
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:38,960
you've got some secret in Kangcheng?

151
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:40,840
Kangcheng is Liu Heng's fiefdom

152
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,360
I just don't want trouble

153
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:44,120
Liu Heng has a fiefdom?

154
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,080
He may be an adopted son

155
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:49,000
but Brother Twenty-Eight is still a Prince

156
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:50,879
Let's go

157
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,200
Welcome, guests, come on in

158
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:58,120
Innkeeper

159
00:09:58,759 --> 00:09:59,720
Got any rooms left?

160
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:00,519
Ah

161
00:10:00,519 --> 00:10:01,360
Yes, we do

162
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,480
Only two rooms left

163
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,960
You young couple take one

164
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:08,399
This gentleman takes the other

165
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,279
We're not a couple

166
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:11,080
Exactly

167
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:13,080
Who'd be a couple with this dimwit?

168
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:13,799
Oh dear

169
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,440
I've run this inn for over twenty years

170
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,000
Guess I misjudged today

171
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:18,559
Oh dear

172
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:19,120
My apologies

173
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:19,840
So sorry

174
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,200
Actually

175
00:10:21,279 --> 00:10:23,000
those two are the ones getting married soon

176
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:25,679
How about you two share for tonight?

177
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:26,679
This princess will sleep alone

178
00:10:26,799 --> 00:10:27,600
You two figure it out

179
00:10:38,159 --> 00:10:38,960
Hey

180
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:45,559
Envoy

181
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,360
Hmm?

182
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,039
I wanted to ask you something

183
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:50,720
Just now, did I

184
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:52,039
do something wrong?

185
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:53,559
Not at all

186
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:55,440
You were perfectly courteous

187
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,480
What could you have done wrong?

188
00:10:58,279 --> 00:10:59,360
Then why

189
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,399
did she suddenly get so angry?

190
00:11:02,759 --> 00:11:04,519
The Yan people just have peculiar temperaments

191
00:11:04,519 --> 00:11:05,320
Don't mind it

192
00:11:06,919 --> 00:11:08,799
Sorry you had to endure this

193
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,399
The main reason is

194
00:11:10,399 --> 00:11:13,279
the Late Emperor's killer hasn't been found yet

195
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:15,360
So the Crown Prince specifically ordered me

196
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:17,440
to be cautious and keep a low profile

197
00:11:18,159 --> 00:11:18,759
Alright

198
00:11:18,759 --> 00:11:19,960
You get some rest then

199
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,679
I'll step out for some air

200
00:11:21,679 --> 00:11:22,480
Hey

201
00:11:32,639 --> 00:11:33,440
Who is it?

202
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,399
Me

203
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:37,080
And who are you?

204
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,600
What do you want?

205
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,799
If nothing, I'm going to rest

206
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:43,960
I do have something

207
00:11:48,559 --> 00:11:49,360
Speak

208
00:11:51,279 --> 00:11:52,360
Let me come in to talk

209
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,799
No way

210
00:11:53,799 --> 00:11:56,320
A man and woman alone in a room late at night?

211
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,320
That's hardly proper

212
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,399
Then come out and say it

213
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,240
I won't

214
00:12:01,919 --> 00:12:04,320
This princess is already betrothed

215
00:12:04,639 --> 00:12:06,559
Why are you so worked up?

216
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,799
Do you have something to say or not?

217
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,320
I did, but not anymore

218
00:12:11,799 --> 00:12:12,600
Wait

219
00:12:15,159 --> 00:12:17,919
This princess wants to go out for a stroll

220
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,639
I'll give you a chance to come along

221
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:29,159
You've done the Crown Prince such a huge favor

222
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:32,799
Things should be easier for you when you return, right?

223
00:12:33,919 --> 00:12:35,559
I don't plan to stay in the palace

224
00:12:37,559 --> 00:12:38,360
Why not?

225
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:41,159
That's been my plan from the start

226
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:43,440
I figured once this mission was done

227
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,919
I'd take Huahua and leave the capital

228
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,759
Looks like

229
00:12:46,879 --> 00:12:48,919
that wish will come true soon enough

230
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,039
No

231
00:12:50,559 --> 00:12:51,360
Ah

232
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,440
Uh

233
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:55,759
I mean

234
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,519
Well

235
00:12:59,519 --> 00:13:00,320
What I mean is

236
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,840
You at least have to attend

237
00:13:03,039 --> 00:13:05,519
my wedding with the Prince of Chen before leaving

238
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,279
Oh

239
00:13:18,159 --> 00:13:18,960
Hey

240
00:13:19,759 --> 00:13:20,399
Uh

241
00:13:20,399 --> 00:13:23,000
You won't quit till you're Empress, will you?

242
00:13:23,799 --> 00:13:24,600
Besides,

243
00:13:25,159 --> 00:13:26,919
Huahua's still with you. What are you afraid of?

244
00:13:31,879 --> 00:13:32,679
Hey

245
00:13:34,559 --> 00:13:35,960
You came to see me.

246
00:13:36,919 --> 00:13:37,919
Could it be

247
00:13:39,799 --> 00:13:41,720
you came to take Huahua back?

248
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,279
Actually, I just came to see

249
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,039
Huahua.

250
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:52,919
Oh.

251
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,120
Wait here a moment.

252
00:14:07,039 --> 00:14:07,840
Here.

253
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:22,799
I'm giving her back.

254
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:25,639
Huahua.

255
00:14:27,559 --> 00:14:28,679
Are you angry?

256
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:29,919
Not at all.

257
00:14:30,879 --> 00:14:32,320
Huahua was yours to begin with.

258
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:34,799
I just kept her to threaten you.

259
00:14:36,039 --> 00:14:38,480
Since the Prince of Chen agreed to make me Empress,

260
00:14:38,919 --> 00:14:40,320
naturally I'll return Huahua to you.

261
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:43,480
Hey,

262
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:45,679
if you can can't bear to part with her,

263
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,399
you

264
00:14:46,399 --> 00:14:47,919
can return her after we're back at the palace.

265
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:53,639
This chicken's so dumb.

266
00:14:54,039 --> 00:14:55,480
I'm not reluctant at all.

267
00:14:56,639 --> 00:14:58,000
I'm going back to rest.

268
00:15:03,639 --> 00:15:04,919
Since you're leaving,

269
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:06,559
I don't have much to give you.

270
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,399
Take this dagger,

271
00:15:08,679 --> 00:15:09,480
keep it for self-defense.

272
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:10,279
Ah!

273
00:15:30,919 --> 00:15:31,360
Oh no!

274
00:15:31,519 --> 00:15:31,759
Hua...

275
00:15:31,759 --> 00:15:32,279
Hey!

276
00:15:34,159 --> 00:15:34,759
Huahua!

277
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,200
Huahua!

278
00:15:38,279 --> 00:15:39,879
Huahua!

279
00:15:39,879 --> 00:15:40,399
Come out!

280
00:15:40,399 --> 00:15:40,879
Huahua!

281
00:15:41,879 --> 00:15:43,279
Cluck cluck cluck cluck!

282
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:44,360
Hey, Envoy Qi.

283
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:45,799
What are you doing so early in the morning?

284
00:15:45,799 --> 00:15:46,559
Have you seen my Huahua?

285
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:47,559
Huahua!

286
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:48,360
Huahua!

287
00:15:48,360 --> 00:15:49,639
Cluck cluck cluck cluck!

288
00:15:49,879 --> 00:15:50,320
Oh, crap!

289
00:15:50,799 --> 00:15:51,159
Oh, crap!

290
00:15:51,639 --> 00:15:52,279
Cluck cluck cluck cluck!

291
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:54,919
What are you doing?

292
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:56,279
Did you take Huahua back last night?

293
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:57,279
No, I didn't.

294
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:01,600
Huahua's gone!

295
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:03,799
What?

296
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:05,559
She doesn't have any luggage,

297
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:06,879
no money,

298
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,440
and no food.

299
00:16:10,519 --> 00:16:12,639
I just gave you Huahua last night,

300
00:16:12,639 --> 00:16:14,080
and you lost her already?

301
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:15,120
I'll go out and look.

302
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:18,399
Huahua!

303
00:16:18,879 --> 00:16:19,799
What are you looking for?

304
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:20,960
Hey, hey!

305
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:21,960
Huahua, Huahua, Huahua!

306
00:16:22,639 --> 00:16:23,960
Did they mistreat you, Huahua?

307
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:25,840
Long time no see,

308
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,639
Crown Prince.

309
00:16:31,399 --> 00:16:32,360
Is it really that serious?

310
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:33,279
I didn't do anything to it.

311
00:16:33,279 --> 00:16:34,080
Don't bother me.

312
00:16:35,159 --> 00:16:35,840
What are you doing?

313
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:37,360
I'm counting Huahua's feathers.

314
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:39,799
Let me tell you.

315
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,200
Don't joke around with Huahua.

316
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:43,320
Otherwise I'll, I'll, I'll...

317
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:44,200
I'll tear up your comic books.

318
00:16:44,799 --> 00:16:45,120
Tch.

319
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:47,039
Fine, I won't touch it.

320
00:16:47,039 --> 00:16:48,399
As if I wanted to anyway.

321
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:50,399
Huahua, let's go.

322
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:51,759
Where to?

323
00:16:51,799 --> 00:16:53,159
Huahua's been frightened inside.

324
00:16:53,279 --> 00:16:54,559
I'm taking it out for a walk.

325
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:56,000
Oh my, my.

326
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:56,919
Hurry up and take it away.

327
00:16:57,919 --> 00:16:58,240
I'm coming too.

328
00:17:01,639 --> 00:17:02,279
Royal Brother.

329
00:17:02,639 --> 00:17:04,400
I came all the way from the palace to meet you,

330
00:17:04,640 --> 00:17:05,799
and he doesn't even appreciate it.

331
00:17:08,799 --> 00:17:09,799
If you ask me,

332
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,400
you couldn't stand being in the palace,

333
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:12,759
so you ran out on your own, right?

334
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:15,240
I'm just eager

335
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,599
to abdicate the throne to you, Royal Brother.

336
00:17:19,720 --> 00:17:20,119
Hey.

337
00:17:20,119 --> 00:17:21,559
But then again,

338
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:25,319
I've never seen anyone treat a chicken so seriously.

339
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:27,160
It's truly unbelievable.

340
00:17:27,799 --> 00:17:28,759
What's so strange about it?

341
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:30,160
Royal Brother, you...

342
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:32,599
You can treat something as boring as Go

343
00:17:32,599 --> 00:17:34,000
as more important than your own life.

344
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:35,720
At least Huahua is a living creature.

345
00:17:36,119 --> 00:17:36,759
Right?

346
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:40,599
Go is profound and intricate.

347
00:17:41,119 --> 00:17:42,839
Crown Prince, how could you call it boring?

348
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:44,440
Royal Brother.

349
00:17:44,839 --> 00:17:46,039
Profound it may be,

350
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,880
but that doesn't stop it from being boring.

351
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:48,480
Right?

352
00:17:51,160 --> 00:17:52,079
And aren't you the one

353
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:54,960
who, for some lowbrow thing like comics,

354
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:57,079
abandoned the Great Liang's empire?

355
00:17:57,839 --> 00:17:58,640
Royal Brother, you...

356
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:02,359
I just said your Go was boring,

357
00:18:02,559 --> 00:18:04,400
and you actually called my comics lowbrow?

358
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,079
As for my comics,

359
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:10,519
I can draw your Go game with a single brush.

360
00:18:10,519 --> 00:18:11,200
Can you do the same?

361
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:12,279
Why couldn't I?

362
00:18:12,839 --> 00:18:13,240
Uh.

363
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:13,559
Waiter!

364
00:18:14,079 --> 00:18:14,559
Bring the Go board.

365
00:18:14,799 --> 00:18:14,920
Tch.

366
00:18:15,599 --> 00:18:16,400
Come off it, Royal Brother.

367
00:18:16,839 --> 00:18:19,319
Your Go pieces are all round little things.

368
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:20,240
How are you going to arrange them?

369
00:18:22,519 --> 00:18:23,720
The pieces are black and white,

370
00:18:24,039 --> 00:18:25,359
and paper and ink are also black and white.

371
00:18:25,599 --> 00:18:27,319
I'll show you how it's done today.

372
00:18:27,359 --> 00:18:28,000
Fine.

373
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:29,000
I'd love to see how you pull this off.

374
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:30,039
Waiter!

375
00:18:30,039 --> 00:18:30,480
Bring the Go board.

376
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:31,759
Waiter!

377
00:18:32,079 --> 00:18:32,880
Where's the waiter?

378
00:18:38,599 --> 00:18:41,240
Since you're both so obsessed with these trivial pursuits,

379
00:18:41,799 --> 00:18:43,240
why don't I be the emperor?

380
00:18:43,839 --> 00:18:45,880
You two can just paint and play Go.

381
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:46,960
Little Twenty-Eight.

382
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:48,680
What's he doing here?

383
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:49,839
Everyone else, get out.

384
00:18:50,279 --> 00:18:55,440
Oh my, go, go, go.

385
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:57,039
Little Twenty-Eight,

386
00:18:57,039 --> 00:18:58,079
what are you here for?

387
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:59,279
I'm here to help you.

388
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:00,799
Hmph.

389
00:19:01,599 --> 00:19:03,200
If you want the throne, just say so.

390
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:05,599
You've already made this big a scene,

391
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:08,279
so stop beating around the bush.

392
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:11,440
My two dear brothers,

393
00:19:12,119 --> 00:19:14,079
since neither of you wants to be emperor,

394
00:19:14,279 --> 00:19:16,880
why not just hand the throne over to me?

395
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:18,599
Among us brothers,

396
00:19:18,599 --> 00:19:20,079
isn't it perfect to each take what we need?

397
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:21,480
Why slaughter each other?

398
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:22,279
Absurd.

399
00:19:23,759 --> 00:19:25,839
The throne isn't something to hand over on a whim.

400
00:19:25,839 --> 00:19:27,079
Is this some child's game?

401
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:29,599
Since the Crown Prince has already chosen me,

402
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:31,480
I must shoulder this responsibility.

403
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:32,440
Exactly.

404
00:19:35,759 --> 00:19:36,880
Liars!

405
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,240
You're all liars!

406
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:42,039
It's just because I'm Imperial Father's adopted son,

407
00:19:42,119 --> 00:19:43,720
that's why you've looked down on me since childhood.

408
00:19:45,319 --> 00:19:47,279
All my life,

409
00:19:47,279 --> 00:19:49,960
all my life, I've never felt any brotherly love.

410
00:19:51,799 --> 00:19:53,440
Little Twenty-Eight,

411
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:54,440
why are you crying now?

412
00:19:54,599 --> 00:19:55,160
I...

413
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:55,960
Hey.

414
00:19:56,319 --> 00:19:57,400
How about this,

415
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,279
what do you want to eat?

416
00:19:58,279 --> 00:19:59,240
I'll order it for you.

417
00:19:59,319 --> 00:20:00,200
I don't want any.

418
00:20:03,079 --> 00:20:03,799
Then I'll...

419
00:20:03,799 --> 00:20:05,200
I'll lend you my comic books.

420
00:20:05,279 --> 00:20:06,839
Who wants your lousy comics?

421
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,400
Then what do you want?

422
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:09,559
I...

423
00:20:10,200 --> 00:20:11,920
All I want is some assurance, is that so hard?

424
00:20:14,799 --> 00:20:15,599
Assurance?

425
00:20:15,599 --> 00:20:16,640
That's easy.

426
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:18,079
I'll give you some assurance.

427
00:20:19,039 --> 00:20:19,839
Really?

428
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:20,279
Yeah,

429
00:20:20,279 --> 00:20:21,400
I can assure you that you have no chance.

430
00:20:25,920 --> 00:20:27,400
You forced me into this!

431
00:20:27,839 --> 00:20:28,799
Guards!

432
00:20:28,799 --> 00:20:29,640
Seize them!

433
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:30,359
Hey!

434
00:20:30,359 --> 00:20:30,759
You...

435
00:20:30,759 --> 00:20:31,559
Don't move!

436
00:20:37,720 --> 00:20:38,519
Hey

437
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:41,559
There's nobody around here

438
00:20:42,079 --> 00:20:44,079
You don't need to be so tense

439
00:20:45,079 --> 00:20:47,279
I feel someone's plotting against our Huahua

440
00:20:48,559 --> 00:20:49,079
Oh, please

441
00:20:49,519 --> 00:20:51,279
I think no one in this world but you

442
00:20:51,359 --> 00:20:53,319
would be interested in a chicken

443
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:54,960
Nonsense

444
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:56,839
Our Huahua is super popular

445
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,160
Isn't that right, Huahua?

446
00:20:59,240 --> 00:20:59,480
Oh my

447
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:01,519
All those little butterflies and snails

448
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:02,680
love playing with our Huahua

449
00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:03,599
Ah

450
00:21:03,599 --> 00:21:03,960
Oh dear

451
00:21:03,960 --> 00:21:04,400
Tsk, tsk, tsk

452
00:21:05,119 --> 00:21:05,920
Hmm

453
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:06,960
Scary

454
00:21:07,680 --> 00:21:10,319
She's even ready to fight at any moment

455
00:21:13,359 --> 00:21:13,720
Come

456
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:15,519
Let me teach you a move

457
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:17,480
Oh

458
00:21:18,519 --> 00:21:19,319
Look

459
00:21:19,960 --> 00:21:21,079
When you meet an enemy,

460
00:21:21,319 --> 00:21:22,119
draw your blade first

461
00:21:22,839 --> 00:21:23,960
Swing it at his neck

462
00:21:25,119 --> 00:21:26,799
The neck is a vital spot

463
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:29,799
Just swing at his neck

464
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:32,519
and he'll lean back for sure

465
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:34,680
His lower body becomes exposed

466
00:21:35,319 --> 00:21:38,240
Then you kick him in the lower body

467
00:21:39,079 --> 00:21:40,240
He's guaranteed to fall

468
00:21:41,799 --> 00:21:42,680
Then what?

469
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:44,680
Once he falls,

470
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:46,000
you just run

471
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:48,400
That's it

472
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:50,599
Don't underestimate this move

473
00:21:50,759 --> 00:21:52,480
It can save your life in a pinch

474
00:21:53,759 --> 00:21:54,720
Besides,

475
00:21:55,839 --> 00:21:58,119
when I'm not around in the future,

476
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:00,640
if you ever run into danger,

477
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:04,559
this might just save your life

478
00:22:06,079 --> 00:22:06,680
Here

479
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:07,200
Give it a try

480
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:12,279
Draw the blade

481
00:22:12,279 --> 00:22:13,079
Hmm

482
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:15,200
Hey

483
00:22:20,200 --> 00:22:21,000
Hey

484
00:22:22,519 --> 00:22:23,880
Why can't I pull it out?

485
00:22:23,880 --> 00:22:24,680
Can't even draw your blade

486
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:26,359
How will you save your Huahua?

487
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:27,960
Hey, Huahua

488
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:28,319
Huahua

489
00:22:28,319 --> 00:22:28,920
Hey

490
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:29,559
Huahua

491
00:22:31,319 --> 00:22:31,720
Stop right there

492
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:32,519
Huahua

493
00:22:32,799 --> 00:22:33,640
Ah

494
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:34,359
Huahua

495
00:22:34,359 --> 00:22:35,599
Huahua

496
00:22:35,799 --> 00:22:36,519
Ah, hey

497
00:22:40,119 --> 00:22:41,480
I knew it was you

498
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:43,359
Heh

499
00:22:45,000 --> 00:22:46,240
After tailing you for so long,

500
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:48,559
today you finally fell into my hands

501
00:22:48,559 --> 00:22:49,799
This is sixty li from your fief

502
00:22:49,799 --> 00:22:50,640
How did you find us?

503
00:22:52,759 --> 00:22:53,400
Me?

504
00:22:53,400 --> 00:22:56,559
I already put up wanted posters all over town

505
00:22:57,599 --> 00:22:58,599
Hey

506
00:22:58,599 --> 00:22:59,680
Who would say no to money?

507
00:23:00,599 --> 00:23:01,559
Hahahaha

508
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:05,720
Here

509
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:06,440
Oh my

510
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:07,599
Thank you

511
00:23:07,599 --> 00:23:08,200
Hahaha

512
00:23:17,279 --> 00:23:18,559
Give me the Late Emperor's jade pendant.

513
00:23:18,559 --> 00:23:19,640
Let them go first.

514
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:20,960
You big idiot.

515
00:23:21,599 --> 00:23:22,200
Hey!

516
00:23:22,799 --> 00:23:24,359
This is Liu Heng's turf.

517
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:25,839
And you dare bargain with me?

518
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:27,319
Hmph.

519
00:23:27,319 --> 00:23:28,119
Uh, thank you, Prince.

520
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:30,759
At the price we agreed on,

521
00:23:30,799 --> 00:23:32,000
three hundred taels a day,

522
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:34,599
drinks half-off, but room and board still apply.

523
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:35,519
Right?

524
00:23:36,200 --> 00:23:36,960
Got it.

525
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:38,279
Come by my residence later to collect it.

526
00:23:38,279 --> 00:23:38,759
No, wait.

527
00:23:39,079 --> 00:23:41,839
You have to give me 250 taels as a deposit first.

528
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:47,799
Boss.

529
00:23:49,559 --> 00:23:50,559
Otherwise,

530
00:23:51,559 --> 00:23:53,200
how about I give you this chicken?

531
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:53,960
No way!

532
00:23:54,559 --> 00:23:55,200
If you dare lay a finger on Huahua,

533
00:23:55,200 --> 00:23:56,640
I'll, I'll, I'll rip up your comic books!

534
00:23:56,799 --> 00:23:57,480
Ah, ah, ah, no.

535
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:58,920
I'll, I'll...

536
00:23:58,920 --> 00:23:59,920
smash the Late Emperor's jade pendant!

537
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:00,880
Let's see what you do then.

538
00:24:05,599 --> 00:24:06,720
You two, write him an IOU.

539
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:07,799
Yes, sir.

540
00:24:08,039 --> 00:24:08,920
Alright, sure.

541
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:09,960
This way, please.

542
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:12,240
Hey!

543
00:24:12,240 --> 00:24:13,240
If you know what's good for you,

544
00:24:13,519 --> 00:24:15,200
bring me the Late Emperor's jade pendant.

545
00:24:19,279 --> 00:24:20,079
Okay.

546
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:21,000
Don't give it to him!

547
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:25,400
I'll count to three,

548
00:24:26,319 --> 00:24:27,240
and we throw at the same time.

549
00:24:29,359 --> 00:24:30,519
Deal.

550
00:24:31,839 --> 00:24:32,200
Hey!

551
00:24:32,559 --> 00:24:33,079
Come here.

552
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:34,720
On three,

553
00:24:35,799 --> 00:24:36,839
toss that chicken over.

554
00:24:36,960 --> 00:24:37,480
One.

555
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:40,200
Two.

556
00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:43,039
Three!

557
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:44,480
Don't move!

558
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:46,039
What are you doing?!

559
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:47,440
If you dare move an inch,

560
00:24:48,039 --> 00:24:50,839
I'll have her smash the Late Emperor's jade pendant!

561
00:24:51,319 --> 00:24:52,440
Hey, no, no, no!

562
00:25:02,279 --> 00:25:03,559
He moved a couple of times.

563
00:25:07,759 --> 00:25:09,119
What's wrong with you?

564
00:25:09,759 --> 00:25:10,559
I...

565
00:25:12,960 --> 00:25:15,440
The Late Emperor's jade pendant is already broken.

566
00:25:15,559 --> 00:25:16,400
I can't be bothered with you.

567
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:17,640
Ganging up on me!

568
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:18,480
Have you no shame?

569
00:25:19,480 --> 00:25:21,119
Fight this princess one-on-one if you dare!

570
00:25:21,480 --> 00:25:22,279
Hey!

571
00:25:22,279 --> 00:25:23,319
Sister Ouyang.

572
00:25:23,599 --> 00:25:24,880
Are you out of your mind?

573
00:25:25,880 --> 00:25:27,359
Saying I'm ganging up on you?

574
00:25:27,359 --> 00:25:28,400
Think about it yourselves.

575
00:25:28,559 --> 00:25:30,839
When haven't you all ganged up to bully me?

576
00:25:31,279 --> 00:25:32,640
Now you wanna play fair with me?

577
00:25:32,680 --> 00:25:33,720
Where was that fairness before?

578
00:25:34,599 --> 00:25:35,400
Tch.

579
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:36,920
He's got a point.

580
00:25:40,319 --> 00:25:41,440
I really don't get it.

581
00:25:42,240 --> 00:25:44,519
Why did Imperial Father adopt you back then?

582
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:47,200
Royal Brother.

583
00:25:47,799 --> 00:25:48,680
You don't need to understand.

584
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:51,200
Once I become emperor,

585
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:52,799
you'll find out soon enough.

586
00:25:53,480 --> 00:25:54,440
So...

587
00:25:54,799 --> 00:25:55,759
I absolutely,

588
00:25:56,200 --> 00:25:56,960
absolutely,

589
00:25:57,160 --> 00:25:59,279
absolutely will not send you back to the capital.

590
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:00,559
Heh heh heh.

591
00:26:05,079 --> 00:26:05,880
Royal Brother.

592
00:26:06,440 --> 00:26:08,960
Now that the Late Emperor's pendant is broken,

593
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,960
I'll have to ask you to cede the throne to me.

594
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:15,799
If we go by order of succession,

595
00:26:16,359 --> 00:26:18,279
none of the previous princes can take the throne.

596
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:20,440
I really should cede the throne to you.

597
00:26:21,519 --> 00:26:22,920
But today,

598
00:26:22,920 --> 00:26:24,359
you stopped at nothing for the throne,

599
00:26:24,599 --> 00:26:26,079
and even tried to harm my elder brother.

600
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:29,200
I will absolutely never cede it to you.

601
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:31,960
You've been rambling on and on.

602
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:32,599
What are you even saying?

603
00:26:32,599 --> 00:26:33,599
Might as well have said nothing.

604
00:26:34,039 --> 00:26:34,599
Hey.

605
00:26:34,599 --> 00:26:35,480
Think about it.

606
00:26:35,680 --> 00:26:37,680
If I, Liu Heng, hadn't fought for it,

607
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:39,640
would the throne ever come to me?

608
00:26:40,079 --> 00:26:40,519
What?

609
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:42,119
Nothing to say now?

610
00:26:42,599 --> 00:26:43,480
Gone silent?

611
00:26:44,480 --> 00:26:45,279
Fine.

612
00:26:45,799 --> 00:26:47,960
Then I'll just have to force you to abdicate.

613
00:26:47,960 --> 00:26:49,319
Heh heh heh heh.

614
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:50,559
What do you mean by that?

615
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:52,759
Guards!

616
00:27:02,559 --> 00:27:03,279
Hey

617
00:27:03,279 --> 00:27:04,079
What are you doing?

618
00:27:08,039 --> 00:27:08,839
Twenty-Eight

619
00:27:10,319 --> 00:27:11,559
He is your brother, you know.

620
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:13,200
I've said it before,

621
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:14,920
I won't let him go.

622
00:27:20,799 --> 00:27:21,279
Hey!

623
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:22,880
Help!

624
00:27:23,200 --> 00:27:23,839
Help me!

625
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:27,119
Every hour,

626
00:27:27,119 --> 00:27:29,160
I'll have someone swap out this sandbag.

627
00:27:29,599 --> 00:27:31,640
Until the sand buries you alive.

628
00:27:32,279 --> 00:27:33,599
So before that happens,

629
00:27:33,599 --> 00:27:35,759
you have plenty of time to think it over.

630
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:38,240
Whether he lives or dies,

631
00:27:38,599 --> 00:27:39,559
it's all up to you.

632
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:40,319
Liu Heng,

633
00:27:40,319 --> 00:27:41,799
didn't you say that no matter what,

634
00:27:42,079 --> 00:27:43,359
you'd never harm your own kin?

635
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:43,759
Hey!

636
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:45,640
How did I become like this?

637
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:47,200
You're the ones who drove me to it!

638
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:48,799
Let me tell you,

639
00:27:48,799 --> 00:27:50,480
even if he really dies here today,

640
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:51,599
it won't be me, Liu Heng, who killed him.

641
00:27:51,599 --> 00:27:52,799
It'll be because you didn't save him.

642
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:54,480
Then what will it take for you to let us go?

643
00:27:56,960 --> 00:27:57,519
It's simple.

644
00:27:58,519 --> 00:28:00,160
You just need to issue an Imperial Edict.

645
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,559
And on that edict,

646
00:28:01,559 --> 00:28:02,200
just write

647
00:28:02,920 --> 00:28:03,559
that you are foolish,

648
00:28:03,839 --> 00:28:04,920
that you are stupid,

649
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,039
and uglier than me.

650
00:28:07,759 --> 00:28:10,039
Then proclaim to all that I'll be Emperor.

651
00:28:10,519 --> 00:28:11,240
And I

652
00:28:11,759 --> 00:28:12,640
will release you immediately.

653
00:28:13,599 --> 00:28:14,880
Look at the state he's in.

654
00:28:15,039 --> 00:28:16,359
He probably won't last much longer.

655
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,000
You decide what to do.

656
00:28:18,079 --> 00:28:18,480
Help!

657
00:28:18,920 --> 00:28:19,480
Help me!

658
00:28:19,720 --> 00:28:19,920
Hey!

659
00:28:20,279 --> 00:28:21,119
Give Huahua back to me first.

660
00:28:22,640 --> 00:28:23,440
Don't worry.

661
00:28:24,039 --> 00:28:26,640
Once my dear Royal Brother lets me be Emperor,

662
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:29,559
not just your people,

663
00:28:29,759 --> 00:28:30,599
but every one of your people

664
00:28:30,799 --> 00:28:31,440
and even your chickens,

665
00:28:32,039 --> 00:28:33,680
I won't harm a single hair on them.

666
00:28:34,039 --> 00:28:34,960
Heh heh heh heh heh.

667
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:35,920
Let's go!
